EA UPDATE

The @EnvAgency have issued an update this evening, ahead of the midnight deadline.

We are eagerly awaiting you engaging with us ASAP.
@StinkStopthe https://t.co/L05ZKwEmf7

5/5 Lastly: üôè to those who kindly came to share experiences of living with this odour.
